# Phase A guardrail (2026-07-16): prevents recurrence of the tooling debris documented in
# packages/knowledge-engine/README.md §5/§8. This does NOT untrack anything already committed —
# the existing .npm_cache/ under legacy-archive/scratch/ (and its duplicate under
# knowledge-engine/legacy-archive/scratch/) remain tracked pending a later, evidence-backed
# migration decision. This only stops *new* copies of the same noise from being committed again.

# npm/npx cache artifacts (e.g. from `npx antigravity-awesome-skills` or similar tooling runs)
.npm_cache/
.npm/
npm-debug.log*

# Python cache/build artifacts from the generation pipeline scripts
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Local temporary/scratch files
*.tmp
*.temp
.DS_Store
